<article>
  <h3>Angry Penne</h3>
  <img src="images/menu.jpg" alt="Angry Penne Shrimp Pasta">
  <p>Angry Penne is an Italian restaurant located in Garapan. It offers a variety of dishes from pastas, pizza, and desserts as well. The atmosphere there is also very relaxing and the customer service is always top-notch.</p>
  <h4>What I Love:</h4>
  <ul>
    <li>Their Penne Aribiata</li>
    <li>Their Margarita Pizza</li>
    <li>The friendly customer service</li>
  </ul>
